title: MR Sakubasu (EngSub)
description:
3DCG animation

WMV format (118 minutes)
HD resolution (1280x1024 pixels)

STORY
Explorers find a never-before-seen Elvish ruins near a village, where a treasure of countless crystal diamonds is discovered. But something's amiss. Entombed in the beautiful crystals of this unknown place are the corpses of women. The explorers take a sample. Hours later, the entire population of the village has disappeared. What happened? An elite military unit led by Tassyu is called in to find the answer.
